 Times</i>. May 10, 2013.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStacy+Schiff&amp;rft.atitle=Eternal+Flame+%E2%80%93+%E2%80%98Country+Girl%3A+A+Memoir%2C%E2%80%99+by+Edna+O%E2%80%99Brien&amp;rft.date=2013-05-10&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+York+Times&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2013%2F05%2F12%2Fbooks%2Freview%2Fcountry-girl-a-memoir-by-edna-obrien.html%3Fpagewanted%3Dall%26_r%3D0&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2005/06/15/opinion/15schiff.html?_r=0">"The Interactive Truth"</a>. <i>New York Times</i>. June 15, 2005.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStacy+Schiff&amp;rft.atitle=The+Interactive+Truth&amp;rft.date=2005-06-15&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+York+Times&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2005%2F06%2F15%2Fopinion%2F15schiff.html%3F_r%3D0&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/19/books/review/nathan-englanders-new-collection.html?pagewanted=all&amp;_r=0">"Camp Stories (review of Nathan Englander\'s What We Talk About When We Talk About Anne Frank)"</a>. <i>New York Times Sunday Book Review</i>. February 16, 2012.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStacy+Schiff&amp;rft.atitle=Camp+Stories+%28review+of+Nathan+Englander%27s+What+We+Talk+About+When+We+Talk+About+Anne+Frank%29&amp;rft.date=2012-02-16&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+York+Times+Sunday+Book+Review&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2012%2F02%2F19%2Fbooks%2Freview%2Fnathan-englanders-new-collection.html%3Fpagewanted%3Dall